data.title: H. P. Lovecraft was born in 1890 in Providence, Rhode Island. He is known for creating supernatural horror fiction about ancient creatures...
data.meta_description:
17 likes, 1 comments - annastriberger on March 19, 2020: "H. P. Lovecraft was born in 1890 in Providence, Rhode Island. He is known for creating supernatural horror fiction about ancient creatures trying to break in to our reality. He recieved little recognition during his lifetime, but was later considered one of the most significant 20th-century horror authors giving rise to the Lovecraftian subgenre of horror fiction. 
#lovecraft #hplovecraft #cthulhu #horror #horrorfiction".
